-- Insert protocols for Capital District REMSCO
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, title, section, content, sourceUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'INTRO', 'Capital District EMS Protocols Introduction', 'General', 'These protocols are not a substitute for good clinical judgment. They are guidelines for prehospital care. EMTs and paramedics must use their training and experience to provide appropriate care for each patient situation.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Capital District REMSCO - Albany Schenectady Rensselaer Saratoga' AND c.state = 'New York' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, title, section, content, sourceUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, '1001', 'Cardiac Arrest - Adult', 'Cardiac', 'Adult Cardiac Arrest Protocol: Begin CPR immediately. Attach AED/monitor. Analyze rhythm. If VF/VT: Defibrillate 200J biphasic. Resume CPR for 2 minutes. Establish IV/IO access. Epinephrine 1mg IV/IO every 3-5 minutes. Amiodarone 300mg IV/IO for refractory VF/VT.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Capital District REMSCO - Albany Schenectady Rensselaer Saratoga' AND c.state = 'New York' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, title, section, content, sourceUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, '1002', 'Cardiac Arrest - Pediatric', 'Pediatric', 'Pediatric Cardiac Arrest Protocol: Begin CPR with 15:2 ratio. Attach monitor. Analyze rhythm. If VF/VT: Defibrillate 2J/kg. Resume CPR. Establish IO access if IV not obtained in 90 seconds. Epinephrine 0.01mg/kg IV/IO every 3-5 minutes.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Capital District REMSCO - Albany Schenectady Rensselaer Saratoga' AND c.state = 'New York' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, title, section, content, sourceUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, '2001', 'Chest Pain - Cardiac', 'Cardiac', 'Chest Pain Protocol: Obtain 12-lead ECG. Aspirin 324mg PO if no contraindications. Nitroglycerin 0.4mg SL if SBP greater than 90. Morphine 2-4mg IV for pain if NTG ineffective. Consider STEMI activation if ST elevation present.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Capital District REMSCO - Albany Schenectady Rensselaer Saratoga' AND c.state = 'New York' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, title, section, content, sourceUrl, createdAt)
